---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
    title="Products - Day Zero Solutions"
    description="Day Zero's products: NutriCare for aged care dietary safety, RestroAI for restaurant operations, and QueueZero for food trucks. Built around Australian regulation."
    canonical="https://day-zero.com.au/products.html"
    bodyClass="light-hero"
>
    <section class="hub-head">
        <div class="container">
            <p class="section-tag">Products</p>
            <h1 class="hub-title">Purpose-built, one industry at a time.</h1>
            <p class="hub-sub">Two flagships in production and one in active development. Each is built end to end, around the regulation, suppliers, and budgets a real operation actually has. Designed, built, and supported in Australia.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="hub">
        <div class="container">

            <!-- NutriCare -->
            <article class="hub-product">
                <div class="hub-main">
                    <span class="product-kicker"><i class="fas fa-heart-pulse"></i> Aged care</span>
                    <h2 class="hub-name">NutriCare</h2>
                    <p class="hub-tagline">The dietary safety and care-intelligence platform for aged care facilities.</p>
                    <p class="hub-desc">NutriCare runs the full path from a resident's dietary profile to the meal on the tray and the evidence in the audit log. It enforces allergen and IDDSI texture safety at the point of order, screens for malnutrition risk, and produces the documentation the strengthened Aged Care Quality Standards now require as a daily obligation rather than an annual scramble.</p>
                    <ul class="product-features hub-features">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Allergen &amp; IDDSI texture conflict detection at the point of order</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Meal ordering, kitchen display, delivery tracking &amp; intake recording</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> MUST screening, weight trends, hydration &amp; SIRS-ready incident logs</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Nutritional risk to ESPEN 2022, GLIM 2019, AND/ASPEN standards</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> NutriAssist AI, family portal, meal photos &amp; two-way messaging</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> FHIR R4 export, 10-role RBAC, multi-site operator dashboard, full audit trail</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <aside class="hub-facts">
                    <h3>At a glance</h3>
                    <dl>
                        <div><dt>Industry</dt><dd>Aged &amp; senior care</dd></div>
                        <div><dt>Status</dt><dd>In production</dd></div>
                        <div><dt>From</dt><dd>A$10 / resident / month</dd></div>
                        <div><dt>Trial</dt><dd>30 days, pilots available</dd></div>
                    </dl>
                    <a href="https://www.nutri-care.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Visit nutri-care.app</a>
                    <a href="/#book-demo" class="btn btn-outline btn-full">Book a demo</a>
                </aside>
            </article>

            <!-- RestroAI -->
            <article class="hub-product">
                <div class="hub-main">
                    <span class="product-kicker product-kicker-mint"><i class="fas fa-utensils"></i> Restaurants</span>
                    <h2 class="hub-name">RestroAI</h2>
                    <p class="hub-tagline">The operating system for independent Australian restaurants and cafes.</p>
                    <p class="hub-desc">RestroAI puts the back office and the floor in one system, tuned to Australian suppliers, GST, and the food-cost maths that decides whether a venue makes money. Procurement, costing, ordering, and compliance stop living in spreadsheets and supplier WhatsApp threads.</p>
                    <ul class="product-features hub-features">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Inventory, suppliers, purchase orders, goods receipts &amp; stock takes</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Invoice OCR &amp; automated 3-way matching (PO, GRN, invoice)</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Recipe costing, menu engineering (stars / dogs) &amp; waste analytics</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Online ordering, QR menus, kitchen display, reservations &amp; loyalty</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Staff roster, clock-in kiosk, payslips &amp; HACCP logs</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Predictive ordering, smart procurement &amp; RestroAI chat on your data</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <aside class="hub-facts">
                    <h3>At a glance</h3>
                    <dl>
                        <div><dt>Industry</dt><dd>Restaurants &amp; cafes</dd></div>
                        <div><dt>Status</dt><dd>In production</dd></div>
                        <div><dt>From</dt><dd>A$49 / month</dd></div>
                        <div><dt>Trial</dt><dd>15 days, no card</dd></div>
                    </dl>
                    <a href="https://restroai.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-mint btn-full">Explore restroai.app</a>
                    <a href="/#book-demo" class="btn btn-outline btn-full">Book a demo</a>
                </aside>
            </article>

            <!-- QueueZero -->
            <article class="hub-product hub-product-emerging">
                <div class="hub-main">
                    <span class="product-kicker product-kicker-orange"><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> In development</span>
                    <h2 class="hub-name">QueueZero</h2>
                    <p class="hub-tagline">Mobile ordering and queue-busting for food trucks and pop-ups.</p>
                    <p class="hub-desc">Customers order ahead and you cook ahead, with no app to download and no hardware to buy. QueueZero is in active development. The foundation cohort is forming now and will get locked-in launch pricing.</p>
                    <p class="hub-planned-label">Planned for launch</p>
                    <ul class="product-features hub-features hub-planned">
                        <li><i class="far fa-circle"></i> Mobile-first ordering, no app install for customers</li>
                        <li><i class="far fa-circle"></i> Live queue visibility and order-ahead scheduling</li>
                        <li><i class="far fa-circle"></i> Menu set up from a photo</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <aside class="hub-facts">
                    <h3>At a glance</h3>
                    <dl>
                        <div><dt>Industry</dt><dd>Food trucks &amp; pop-ups</dd></div>
                        <div><dt>Status</dt><dd>In development</dd></div>
                        <div><dt>Pricing</dt><dd>Tier model at launch</dd></div>
                        <div><dt>Access</dt><dd>Foundation cohort</dd></div>
                    </dl>
                    <a href="/#coming-soon" class="btn btn-orange btn-full">Join the waitlist</a>
                </aside>
            </article>

        </div>
    </section>
</Base>
